  "signal_description": "This SIGNAL query calculates the average duration it takes to close an issue in each month. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-217' table. The 'Month when Issue Closed' column is created by truncating the 'end_time' column to the month level for the first occurrence of the 'Change Status to Closed' event. The 'Duration' column is calculated by subtracting the first occurrence of the 'Change Status to In Progress' event from the last occurrence of the 'Change Status to Closed' event. The result is filtered to include only events where the event_name matches the pattern 'Change Status to In Progress' followed by 'Change Status to Closed'. The results are grouped by the 'Month when Issue Closed' column and ordered by the same column."
